<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.9.5">
<l>vakkaraṉ vāymuṉ kīṇṭa māyaṉē yeṉṟu vāṉōr</l>
<l>pukkaraṇ tanta ruḷā yeṉṉa<supplied>p</supplied>poṉ  ṉākat tāṉai</l>
<l>nakkari yuruva māki nakaṅkiḷarn tiṭantu kanta</l>
<l>cakkarac celvaṉ teṉpērt talaivaṉṟā ḷaṭaintuyn tēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I was saved by taking refuge at the feet of the leader of Pēr in the South,</l>
<l rend="indent">the noble with a discus,</l>
<l>Who, taking the form of a slavering lion, was pleased, unsheathing his claws,</l>
<l rend="indent">gouging into the one with a golden chest,</l>
<l>So that the celestials, saying, “Māyaṉ, who once split</l>
<l rend="indent">[Danta]vakra’s mouth,”</l>
<l>Reaching [him] said, “Have mercy, giving [us] protection.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
